title: Corn and Feta Fritters
directions: Mix flour, eggs, salt, pepper and soda water together until smooth. Stir in corn, mint and crumbled feta. Stand for 10 minutes. Cook spoonfuls in 1⁄2 cm hot oil in a pan over medium heat until golden on each side. Makes about 20.
Serve with sliced avocado and tomato chutney.
ingredients: Prep time:5 mins plus standingCook time:10 - 15 minutesMakes:about 20
